data.name: label2.Text
data.value: * Note: Handwriting recognizers are based on the built-in Tablet PC components available on Windows. To obtain recognizers for other languages, you will need to install additional MUI language packs, which is available on Windows 7 Enterprise and Ultimate editions via Windows Update.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: The majority of notebook computers have an additional Fn key on the keyboard. On some of them, the Fn key will generate a keyboard event, therefore it may be possible to use the Fn key on its own as a hotkey. If it can be used, it will be represented by its keyboard scancode.

data.name: label10.Text
data.value: Drag this icon to a folder or Desktop

data.name: label9.Text
data.value: To automatically run this program at log in, simply drag the above icon to the "Startup" folder.
